  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink251-kilavi">varaiyātu vantoḻukun talaimakaṟku varaivu vēṭṭa tōḻi kūṟiyatu.  </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">What the confidante who desired marriage [for the hero and heroine], told the hero who kept coming without marrying.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink251">
<l>kuṉṟak kuṟava ṉārppi ṉeḻili</l>
<l>nuṇpa laḻituḷi poḻiyu nāṭa</l>
<l>neṭuvaraip paṭappai nummūrk</l>
<l>kaṭuvara laruvi kāṇiṉu maḻumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O man from the land where,</l>
        <l>if the hill-dweller of the hills roars,</l>
        <l>clouds pour forth</l>
        <l rend="indent2">fine, abundant, swelling drops—</l>
        <l rend="space">even if she looks</l>
        <l>at the waterfalls rushing down</l>
        <l>in your village with gardens on the tall mountain,</l>
        <l>she weeps.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
